# Kurate Design System Rules

You are working in the Kurate web app. Full conventions are in AGENTS.md. This file is the quick-reference for inline code generation.

## NEVER Do These

```
❌ bg-[#1A5C4B]          → bg-teal
❌ text-gray-600         → text-muted-foreground
❌ text-[14px]           → text-sm
❌ rounded-2xl           → rounded-card / rounded-button
❌ max-w-[800px]         → container-content
❌ shadow-[0_4px_6px...] → shadow-sm / shadow-md
❌ style={{ color, boxShadow, fontSize }}  → use className
❌ href="/auth/login"    → ROUTES.AUTH.LOGIN
❌ <Link><Button>        → <Button asChild><Link href={ROUTES.x}>
❌ import Link from "next/link"  → from "@/i18n"
❌ useTranslations() in server component  → getTranslations()
❌ "use client" on page.tsx  → extract client parts to sub-component
❌ <div onClick>         → <button> or <a>
```

## Colors

- Semantic (UI): `bg-background`, `text-foreground`, `bg-primary`, `text-primary-foreground`, `bg-muted`, `text-muted-foreground`, `bg-card`, `border-border`
- State: `bg-success-bg text-success-foreground`, `bg-warning-bg text-warning-foreground`, `bg-info-bg text-info-foreground`
- Brand (landing/logo only): `bg-cream`, `bg-ink`, `bg-teal`, `bg-lavender`, `bg-amber`
- Opacity: `text-ink/75` (min for body text), `bg-teal/10`, `border-ink/[0.06]`

## Tokens

| What | Use |
|------|-----|
| Button radius | `rounded-button` |
| Card radius | `rounded-card` |
| Input radius | `rounded-input` |
| Badge radius | `rounded-badge` |
| Pill | `rounded-pill` |
| Page width | `container-page` |
| Content width | `container-content` |
| Shadows | `shadow-xs` `shadow-sm` `shadow-md` `shadow-lg` `shadow-xl` |
| Font | `font-sans` (body) `font-serif` (headlines) `font-mono` (code/meta) |

## Components

```ts
import { buttonVariants, badgeVariants } from "@/lib/variants";  // shared CVA
import { ROUTES } from "@/app/_libs/constants/routes";           // all paths
import { Link } from "@/i18n";                                    // i18n-aware Link
```

## Localization

```ts
// Server component
const t = await getTranslations("namespace");  // from "next-intl/server"

// Client component ("use client")
const t = useTranslations("namespace");        // from "next-intl"
```

## Accessibility

- Framer Motion: `const prefersReducedMotion = useReducedMotion();` — disable `initial`/`whileHover`/`whileInView` when true
- Decorative SVGs/icons: `aria-hidden="true"`
- Marquee/auto-play containers: `aria-hidden="true"`
- Every `<nav>`: `aria-label="Main navigation"`
- Full pages: `<main id="main-content">`

